Definition: harshly ironic or sinister
Example: black humor; a grim joke; grim laughter; fun ranging from slapstick clowning ... to savage mordant wit
Synonyms: grim, noun, attribute, grimness, mordant, harshly, ironic, or, sinister, humor, a, joke, laughter, fun, ranging, from, slapstick, clowning, to, savage, wit
Category: adj.all
